s.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The proposal that we will lay out in the next section will critically rely
 on countries being able to implement `contingent tax policies' on international
 flights in the sense that they can pass laws that automatically cause the
 tax rate that the country applies on international flights to depend on
